# CAF Backend Scope

This repo is the **CAF Backend platform**, not just a review app.

It must host:

1. **Renderer API** — generate assets from JSON (Puppeteer + Handlebars; lives in `services/renderer`)
2. **Template Playground** — preview and test carousel templates
3. **Review Console** — review and approve generated content (Supabase tasks/assets)

The renderer was **migrated** from the standalone caf-renderer project into `services/renderer`. Do not rewrite its core logic; extend it (e.g. `/render-carousel`, `/preview-template`) and keep the same engine for API and playground.

For full architecture, deployment requirements (`RENDERER_BASE_URL`, stable URL, no tunnel dependency), and migration details, see **AGENTS.md** at the repo root.
